text: The Nokia N95 is a mobile phone developed for the Nokia N-series. It was announced in September 2006. It was released on March 31, 2007. Nokia N95 partnered for the black-colored 8GB release on 24 September 2007. The Nokia N95 8GB was announced on 5 April, 2007. The Nokia N95 8GB has a black skin, partnered with two camera and a swipe-able keyboard, which was released on 24 September and 25 September 2007. According to Nokia Tablet Congress, on 8 January 2008, the Nokia N95 has had 1,000 awards. == History == Nokia N93, which was made for Nokia N-series version, developed on September 5th, 2006 at the Nokia Tablet Congress Center four days after that, it was launched. On 25 September 2006, Nokia N95 partners announced the new features for phones. After that, Nokia N95 was awarded 105 awards for the mobile phone. On 3 March 2006, it had 108 and 109 awards. The Nokia N95 released on 31 March 2007.
